Package com.designPatterns.ChainOfResponsibility

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractLogger
    AbstractLogger Class sets NextLogger() LogMessage() of different loggers and defines the level at which the messages would be logged.
    ChainOfResponsibilityDemo
    This class defines Chain of Logger objects On failing of one it forwards the request to the next logger.
    ConsoleLogger
    ConsoleLogger sets level of logging message for the current request handling object and then writes the messages.
    ErrorLogger
    ErrorLogger logs the error with level : ERROR
    FileLogger
    FileLogger logs the messages with level : DEBUG
